Product: Food Safefy Inspection & Management System 
Purpose: 
"Help the public understand whether food is safe, healthy and reliable, enhance the transparency of the food supply chain, reduce information asymmetry, and enable consumers to make healthier choices based on reliable information. "

Who would benefit
"Ordinary consumers, children and families, people with food allergies, patients with chronic diseases, the elderly, schools and hospitals, food producers, regulatory agencies, and the entire public health system. "

What impact made 
"This product can enhance the transparency of food, boost public trust in food safety, help reduce health risks caused by food safety incidents, and encourage enterprises to raise production standards. In the long term,"
"it can promote more standardized food supply chain management, support a healthier social dietary environment, and assist governments and organizations in identifying potential food safety issues earlier."

